    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 2019 Executive Sport Sedan has been meticulously maintained and remains in impressive condition for its mileage. The exterior retains its deep, metallic luster, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with regular highway driving. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of premium leather and polished trim; the seats remain firm and supportive, showing only slight natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All technological features\u2014including the dual-screen infotainment system, premium audio, and driver-assist suite\u2014function exactly as intended. Mechanically, the vehicle is very strong, having received a full synthetic oil change and a comprehensive brake inspection just last month. It drives straight and true, offering the smooth, responsive power delivery expected of a high-end vehicle. This car has been garage-kept, smoke-free, and comes with a complete service history, representing an excellent opportunity for a buyer seeking luxury and reliability.",
